Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI]\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NOni...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[CABAJI] Defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by petty thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWe aren't sneak thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...we're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThe chart of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never ever forgive\Nyou, Shanks, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Who is the Victor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Fruit Power Showdown!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NIn all my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been as mad\Nat someone as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard, Shanks, stole\Ncountless riches from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you\Ntwo are connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can say whatever\NI want about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've earned that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES shouting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The North Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,South Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, and I'm gonna\Nkeep on saying it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm right, clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NOh, you got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna settle this\Nonce and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NGo ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NAll right, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bust you up flashily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NCounter attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[BECKMAN]\NKnock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody but you two\Ncares which is colder,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the North Pole or the South.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,then why don't you go\Nto both and find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now cool it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LOOKOUT]\NA ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[LOOKOUT] Enemy ship to\Nthe north-northeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Get ready! Time to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NYes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I can't wait to plunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem happy, Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NObviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy ships are just like\Nbig floating treasure chests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural for\Npirates to raid 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's some\Ntruth to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You and everyone else\Nhere just don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the pirate's natural hunger and\Ndesire for plundering treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what\Nit means to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWhat's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... a... treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the treasure on the\Nbottom of the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now my life's path is\Nflashily decided! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NHey, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna come\Ncelebrate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a whole lot\Nof really neat stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no map!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't have...\Nanything hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking\Nabout, Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] You said you were gonna\Nleave this ship sometime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NI'm gonna get my own ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then gather a reliable\Ncrew and see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take my time. Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...All as a pirate, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs] What a bunch\Nof sentimental nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NSay what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] I do admire your\Nfighting skill, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't such a softy,\NI'd make you one of my henchmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NYour henchman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have completely different\Noutlooks on life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think we should just\Nfollow our own paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what pirates do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! You think you're such\Nan expert on pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we ever\Nmeet on the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd have to have\Na fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Pirates do that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You never make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you said something about finding\Nsome interesting loot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh yeah, We\Nfound a Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the\Ndifferent fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,are incarnations\Nof the Sea Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, if you eat one,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you gain devil powers\Nbut the sea will hate you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and take your ability to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to be stupid\Nto eat that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NI'd never get that treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on the ocean floor\Nif I couldn't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NBut still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you could\Nsell that fruit for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at least a hundred\Nmillion berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHeh..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I, pirate apprentice Buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,am about to devour\Nthis Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] You gotta\Nlove the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thinking of consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NWell, Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel any differently yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NNo... Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE E]\NAww, was it a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NI'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a real\NDevil Fruit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NYes! That worked flashily well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are so gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I was able to\Ntrick them so easily. [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to jump ship before\Nthey find out the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With the money I get from\Nselling this Devil Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and finding the sunken treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll easily be able to form\Nmy own crew. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NOh, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't steal too much\Nfood from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna\Nmake the cook mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWhew, that was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--[SHANKS] Oh yeah!\N--[BUGGY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain told\Nme to tell ya--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY snorting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY] Damn you, Bastard!\N--[SHANKS] Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NWhat's that piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NAh! Not my map! [screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWhat the?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you lose\Nyour ability to swim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NHey! Hey, What're you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NHelp... Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NI'll save you Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So... are you telling me\Nthat Shanks saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not the point\NI'm trying to get across!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what he did to\Nme I was unable to swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore unable to\Nobtain my sunken treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I had a revelation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I couldn't go underwater,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'd just obtain all\Nthe treasure on dry land!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Using my brand new\NChop-Chop Powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I won't let anyone\Nwho touches my treasure live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Death to those who try to\Npilfer my hard earned treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here you beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY yelling]\N--[NAMI screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! He spotted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance\Nof escaping from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to\Nflashily chop you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY wheezes]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My balls... My balls...\NThat was a cheap shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run off yet,\Nwe're not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? The mayor's never\Nbeen gone for this long before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like a battle\Nwas going on in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot more\Ncannon fire than usual, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to town\Nto check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You all just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still pirates in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous\Nof a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Exactly. That's why\Nyou'll need our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F]\NWhat kind of citizens are we
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if we don't help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have got to find\Nout what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN D]\NYou can't stop us from going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanna do all we\Ncan to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN cheer]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You better drop that treasure\Nand get outta here, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want him\Ncoming after you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the money and go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I leave\Nmy treasure behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY growls] Did you just\Ncall it your treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a thief who\Nsteals from pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just stole\Na lot of treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,from a really annoying one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So that makes this my\Ntreasure now, Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAh! That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pure nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my treasure and just\Nbecause you stole it from me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't make it yours,\Nyou dirty, sneaky thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! What did your\Nparents teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A criminal trying to lecture\Nanother criminal? Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, the day I take\Na morality lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,from you, is the day\NI stop being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're ready\Nfor the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Here comes,\NChop, Chop...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY whimpers, yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] I'd like to see you try\Nto save your friend from me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... He broke up\Ninto smaller pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY] Nami?\N--[NAMI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY grunts]\N--[BUGGY] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCoochie, coochi, coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY laughing]\N--[NAMI screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHe,he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY yells]\N--[NAMI screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See how you like... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY, NAMI screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NDamn it! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NNo, you knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for giving me my\Ntreasure back, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NLet go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my treasure so get\Nyour grubby hands off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me back my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY] Die!\N--[NAMI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY laughing]\N--[LUFFY] I already told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't finished\Ndealing with me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BUGGY groans]\N--[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider that finishing move
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a little gift from\Nthe old mayor guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThanks a lot, I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSure! No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh yeah! The map!\N--My treasure! [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NThis isn't over yet, Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAh! He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you flashily\Ndo this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NAssemble, Chop-Chop Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for these, Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! My parts!\N-[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Way to go thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Now, Gum-Gum...\N--[BUGGY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI win! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That kid sure sent\NCaptain Buggy flyin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, What do we do\Nwithout the captain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NKeep acting unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NGood idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry your hat's all torn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can\Nstill put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got Buggy out of here,\Nso I'm satisfied for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I have time, I'll fix\Nit for you, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I split this into two bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so give me a hand\Nand carry half of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too heavy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, that clown\NBuggy knew quality treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,when he saw it,\Nand now it's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet I can sell this for at\Nleast ten million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NEh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the chart to\Nthe Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You do want it don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou're giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHa! Thanks, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I finally have it!\NA map of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, does this also mean
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be joining me\Nand my pirate crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, no matter what,\NI'll never join a pirate crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging around with you\Nseems profitable enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only joining you...\Ncause it's in my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey, Zoro! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDid we take care of everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And we got a Navigator
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and we got a chart\Nof the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about this.\NI feel light headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Of course you do. It's\Nalways something with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.\NWhat did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?\NYou're the worst of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, let's go\Nhelp the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should wake the old\Nguy up, now that it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CITIZEN D] You there!\N--[NAMI, LUFFY] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not residents\Nof this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNope. And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that\Ncannon fire we heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like there may\Nhave been a battle here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know anything,\Nplease tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, they're just citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that maybe\Nthey were more pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN A]\NOh, no! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN B]\NCan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN C]\NHe's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN E]\NThe pirates definitely did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F]\NHow horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one who\Nkicked that old man's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZENS]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! You didn't have\Nto tell them that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should explain to them\Nso they don't get angry! [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZENS grumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Why exactly\Ndid you knock our
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,mayor out and leave him\Nin the street to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You better explain yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN E] Who are you?\NAre you with the pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] They're getting\Nreally bloodthirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them know that\Nwe're thieves and pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZENS]\NJust as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--Idiot!\N--But it's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN E]\NPirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you ravage our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN D] We won't show you\Nany mercy for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like they're\Nup for a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI gasps]\N--[LUFFY] Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZENS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN D]\NThere's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F] How dare you\Nhurt our beloved mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps] How do you\Nalways make things worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThis is a good town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NEveryone's so mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just because of\Nthe old mayor guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not gonna listen\Nto our side of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're turning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Wait, hold on!\NYou gotta let me know sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F]\NThey ran into the alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]\NChouchou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doggie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--[barking]\N--[CITIZENS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F]\NHey! Move, Chouchou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN D]\NThose three are pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F] You're barking\Nat the wrong people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't he letting\Nus pass through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouchou, get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Chouchou!\N--[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU growls, barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NLater, doggie! [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We only made it\Nbecause of Chouchou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to\Nput up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Does it matter now?\NWe're done here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYeah, Maybe so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey! Is this your boat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing special,\Nbut I guess it'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I stole it from some dumb\Npirates a few days back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN C]\NThat's a big mouth you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI yells]\N--[HENCHMEN] He! He!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We been waitin' for\Nya, ya little thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought you'd run into\Nus here, now didja, girlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHe.He.He.He....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYeah, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A]\NHey, It's not just sort of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're bound together by fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, these are your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to punish\Nthe two of them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time you\Nlearned what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when you steal other\Npeople's stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Ya' hear me?\NTime for your medicine. He.He.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN gasp, scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! He's waking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN D] Ah...\NThank goodness he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN B]\NWhat happened here, Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NWhat in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN B] It was like\Nthis when we got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a few pirates when we\Narrived, but they all ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Where are\Nthe young ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Are you talking\Nabout those three kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're... still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fools. Treating a\Nsenior citizen like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We drove those pirates\Nout of town, Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry\Nabout them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make them pay
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for what they've\Ndone to our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They deserve to be punished\Nfor destroying the peaceful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,town we all worked\Nso hard to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN E]\NYeah! She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[CITIZEN F] There's still\Ntime to go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hurry--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BOODLE] Shut your mouths!\N--[CITIZENS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who's allowed\Nto complain about those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone else\Nbad-mouth them! You hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you protecting\Nthose pirates, Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! They think they can\Njust disappear and that's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I think they were\Nrunning toward the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NDamn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE grumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NThey can't just leave like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of things I\Nwant to say to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAll right! Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NCan I ask you somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Buggy's\Nmark on your sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well this did used\Nto be Buggy's boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Think I should change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NHey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Young ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the old mayor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NI was ready to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready to die,\Nfilled with despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDon't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NDamn you, young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, young ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, young ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no words...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do, Luffy?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you left that\Nbag of treasure back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That bag was worth around\Nfive million berries, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. And they're\Ngonna need that money
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to repair their destroyed town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was my treasure, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how hard\NI worked to steal it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--Why did you do that?\N--[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NStop! I can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat's the whole idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] If you want it,\Njust go back and get it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I can't do that!\NYou go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] No! That's dangerous!\N--[ZORO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I could die, you know?!\N--[ZORO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I don't care!\NAnd if you do that again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I really will throw\Nyou in the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWell, for better or worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,looks like we finally have\Na navigator in our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWow! We actually found land!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Of course we did!\NWe followed the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.66,0:24:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like\Nthere's a village ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.66,0:24:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Hope there's\Na good place to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Yeah,\NI want some meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.58,0:24:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NForget about food, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey, who's he?
